---
import Layout from '../../layouts/Layout.astro';

const title = "Outdoors & Guides";
---

<Layout title={title}>
  <h1>{title}</h1>

  <p>
    Western Montana is built for getting outside, and this is where
    you'll find it: guided trips, local knowledge, and honest
    recommendations for exploring the area with someone who knows it
    well.
  </p>

  <p>
    Right now that means fishing — from float trips on the Blackfoot
    to winter charters on Flathead Lake. More outdoor categories are
    on the way.
  </p>

  <p>
  <a href="/outdoors/fishing/">🎣 Fishing →</a>
</p>
</Layout>